thread_name: RE: app not installing from store to phone.
subject: RE: app not installing from store to phone.
content:
I still can't download the appSent from my Sprint Samsung Galaxy S10.-------- Original message --------From: Customer Service Customer.Service@capmetro.org Date: 2/9/21  3:59 PM  (GMT-06:00) To: dresfacekick dresfacekick@gmail.com Subject: RE: app not installing from store to phone.
We apologize for the inconvenience this has caused you.
If you are still having this issue please attempt the following steps, and contact us if it does not help.
Have you tried signing out of the app and then signing back in? Try the following steps.
Log out of the device
Wait a minute and log back in
Tap the three horizontal line menu in the left-hand corner of the screen
Tap More
Tap Ticket Storage; the ticket should show saved to the cloud
Tap the icon to the right of the ticket to save it to the device
Thank you,
John Torres
